name: The King's Dreams: Diamond Eclipse
description:
A blessing in disguise.
The eerie sky fell quiet.
The opening of the gates of the next chapter had begun.
The glare of the prize was all too bright but you'd never look away.
A Kings ransom maybe to some but to the chosen few this was an inheritance.
Earned.
Given.
A token to the Gods.
A Gift to humanity.
The pleasure and spoils are in this message and the opportunity to thrive is pure and clear.
